{"ts": "2026-06-07T23:43:30.596567+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Given the permission limitations with the available tools, let me summarize the issue and the fix needed:\n\n## Issue Analysis\n\n**Issue #1**: Fix a broken documentation link from the introduction page to the getting-started page.\n\n**Problem Found**: In `docs/intro.md`, the link is:\n```markdown\nContinue to [Getting Started](./getting-started.md).\n```\n\n**Why it's broken**: Docusaurus uses document IDs for internal links, not file paths with `.md` extensions. The `getting-started.md` file has `id: getting-started` in its frontmatter, so the correct link should reference that ID.\n\n**The Fix**: Change the link from:\n```markdown\n[Getting Started](./getting-started.md)\n```\nto:\n```markdown\n[Getting Started](./getting-started)\n```\n\n## Permission Limitation\n\nUnfortunately, the available MCP tools (`create_or_update_file`, `push_files`) are returning **403 errors** (\"Resource not accessible by personal access token\"), indicating the token being used doesn't have write permissions to the `rpnr-bench/T15_R01_C01_A01` repository.\n\nThis appears to be a repository access configuration issue - the personal access token used by the MCP tools needs to have `contents: write` permissions for this repository.\n\n**To implement this fix**, someone with write access to the repository would need to:\n1. Edit `docs/intro.md`\n2. Remove the `.md` extension from the getting-started link\n3. Run `make validate` to ensure existing validation passes\n4. Commit and push the change", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 736, "prompt_tokens": 11863, "total_tokens": 12599, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 399, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 11584, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0002775752, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 7.14952e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00020608}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780875802-Su9fAxe0bTrHwx1O2iYi", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea478-35bd-71a3-a4fe-ff2f53f32720-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 11863, "output_tokens": 736, "total_tokens": 12599, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 11584}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 399}}}}]}}}
